view-layout

linear layout

<LinearLayout
  android:orientation="vertical/horizontal"/>

relative layout

<RelativeLayout>
<Button
android:id="@+id/btn_toast"/>
<ImageView
android:layout above="@id/btn_toast"
android:id="@+id/iv+photo"
/>
</RelativeLayout>

위에꺼는 겹치지 않도록 해주고
밑에꺼는 겹칠수도 있음 
(관련 UI사진은 영상참고)

frame layout

<FrameLayout>
<Button
android:layout_gravity="bottom"
/>
<ImageView
android:layout_gravity="center"
/>
</FrameLayout>
